Our Front Upper Control Arms enhance suspension customisation, which can improve handling, stability, and tyre wear, making them an ideal choice for off-road enthusiasts and those seeking optimised suspension performance.

&nbsp;



 	High quality tubular upper control arms with clevite rubber bushings boost durability over the OEM item



&nbsp;



 	Allows greater suspension travel before the arm catches on trucks lifted up to 2'



&nbsp;



 	Designed to promote a factory-like geometry by keeping the ball joint at the optimum angle after lifting



&nbsp;



 	We recommend suspension alignment after fitting this item to compensate for the alterations to suspension geometry



&nbsp;



 	A must have when lifting your Ranger



